node.text: I’ve now had 4 tarot readings, and every single one has been  insightful! I’m excited to start sharing them with you. Join me and @garyunderpants for our first official week of Tarot Tuesdays with Gwen and Gary — and stay tuned for many more 🔮🕺

node.text: I had such a blast going live for you guys today—I can’t believe I actually sang a little 🤭 I’ve been so shy about sharing my voice but the main reason I’m learning ukulele is to play & sing for you guys. This was a nice little confidence boost ! Thank you to those of you encouraging me, all your support & good vibes mean the world ! I’m vibing high 🥰 & I officially promise to go live MUCH more often 💯 Check out the full livestream on my IGTV and if you like hanging out with me be sure to turn on your post notifications! I’ll be going live with randos this week so let’s see how that goes 😂

node.text:
Unless you’re pizza I can live without you 😋

Bill Murray

Guys I did something new yesterday and improvised a cauliflower pizza how-to video for my subscribers — Without any prep or much knowledge of how to make one 😂

It was kind of sprung on me so I I said fux it and the video turned out sexy but only half-serious, but mostly just funny asf — it’s a landmark video because it planted so many seeds ! It’s the kind of content I cannot wait to shoot more of! Funny and entertaining but still mouthwatering ;)

I wish I could share more of it here but that’s not an option 🤭 Become a subscriber to watch and let me know if I make you laugh :)

node.text:
It’s wild times guys!

Just a friendly reminder to live in the moment today and every day 💯 Lately I’ve been fighting the blues a bit over the sad state of affairs in the world: the 3rd strain, the pressure / divide over vaccination, the effect of the pandemic on the economy, growing censorship, freedoms being threatened and more. It’s valid to be concerned—but it’s also such an energy drain. Things change so rapidly, I have to remind myself that all we have is the moment. We must enjoy it! And spend our precious energy worrying only about controlling our controllables.

As scary as times are, they could be worse. Not sure if that’s the optimist or the pessimist in me talking..

Photos by @rothco.photography 📸 Comment your fave! Best versions for subscribers only 😉
